        <div class="featured-label">Most Read This Month</div>
        <span style="display:inline-block;background:#1a3a5c;color:#fff;font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:800;padding:0.2rem 0.6rem;border-radius:999px;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase;">GAS SAFETY</span>
        <h3>What Is a Gas Safety Certificate? A Liverpool Landlord's Complete Guide</h3>
        <p>Everything Liverpool landlords need to know about the CP12. Who needs one, what is checked, the legal penalties and how to avoid a £6,000 fine. Written by our Gas Safe engineers.</p>
